      "writtenOn": "2026-04-28T15:49:04Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "- If both are supplied we skipping the peeling altogether.\n- If only peeled trait is supplied, we anyway want to peel to apply the fully-peeled trait.\n\nIf fullypeeled is provided and some of the refs aren\u0027t peeled, do you want to trust the caller and write whatever is provided ?",
      "parentUuid": "a38e6fd8_921cb350",
      "revId": "0936d0dfa59edf2b67c56e22d789801ad548af00",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
